#### Technical Stack

* **Framework:** React Native / Expo (using Expo Router for file-based navigation)
* **UI Primitives:** React Native Paper
* **Styling:** NativeWind (`tailwind.config.js`)
* **State Management (Future Phase):** Zustand & TanStack Query (*Do not implement logic yet; focus strictly on UI/UX scaffolding*).

